  "title": "Direct Sales Executive (Copiers, Biz Equipment) JAC",
  "description": "<p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><p>·       Manage existing accounts and establish new customer’s account by cold calling and canvassing.</p><p>·       Conduct sales presentation and prepare sales proposals for sales closure to meet the company’s sales and profit targets.</p><p>·       Conduct product demonstration and training to end users.</p><p>·       Develop and maintain strong relationship with the customers for business growth.</p><p>·       Analyze customer’s business environment and propose suitable workflow and document management solutions.</p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><p>·       Possess GCE ‘O’, ‘A’ Level, Diploma Holder or equivalent.</p><p>·       Preferably, with relevant direct sales experience in Digital Multi-Functional Copier or BusinessEquipment Product.</p><p>·       Good communication and presentation skills.</p><p>·       Resourceful, self-motivated and result-oriented.</p><p>·       Customer-service mind-set and possess strong interpersonal skills.</p><p>·       Good knowledge of Microsoft Office program (e.g., Words, Excel and PowerPoint).</p><p>·       Preferably with own transport.<br /></p><p><strong>Please submit resumes to jason.chow@oaktree.com.sg with the following details in MSWord format:</strong></p><p>- Position applying for</p><p>- Current remuneration</p><p>- Expected remuneration</p><p>- Notice period</p><p><strong>Jason Chow Yew Fai</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No :       06C4642</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No :            R25158800</strong></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
